  "detailed_description": "Mida is a brave adventurer seeking after lost technological artifacts. <br>What kinds of trouble will try to stop her along the way?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1998420/extras/6a9ebead2220b97caed2afbb4625ba86.poster.avif?t=1753553288\" width=194 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1998420/extras/6a9ebead2220b97caed2afbb4625ba86.webm?t=1753553288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1998420/extras/6a9ebead2220b97caed2afbb4625ba86.mp4?t=1753553288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Jump back to the past in an experience influenced by Shareware games of old.<br>Play through 30 levels across 3 episodes, collecting floppy disks,  gemstones, and soda! <br>Access locked doors, hit jump pads, push crates, dodge spiders, hide from snakes, and more!<br><br>Welcome to Mida's Adventure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1998420/extras/dea966f301eef3b71438bb61fd1c90e3.poster.avif?t=1753553288\" width=454 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1998420/extras/dea966f301eef3b71438bb61fd1c90e3.webm?t=1753553288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1998420/extras/dea966f301eef3b71438bb61fd1c90e3.mp4?t=1753553288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
